text: Rusty Rivets is a 2016-20 Canadian CGI children's animated educational preschool television series produced by Jam Filled Toronto and distributed by Spin Master Entertainment and aired on Nickelodeon and the Nick Jr. Channel in the United States and Treehouse TV in Canada. It aired from November 8, 2016 to May 8, 2020. ==References== Category:2016 Canadian television series debuts Category:2020 Canadian television series endings Category:Canadian children's television series
